text:
The Couple Hawkers are super friendly, the lady boss remembers all her regular customers orders, It is always very enjoyable to patronise them. The food taste fantastic especially the mince meat noodles and the special add on meatballs which taste superb.

Their prawn noodles use fresh prawns and not frozen prawns. The stall owners spend an hour plus to peel the shells of over 1000 prawns. 💪💪

👍👍👍😋😋😋🥰🥰🥰
Felt really thirsty after drinking the soup, fish balls I don't think are handmade but factory made.

One of my favorite “must go” noodle shop when I crave for laksa and meat ball noodle… you will never regret it once ya tried it. The shop also serve other varieties such as fishball and prawn noodle… indulge yourself in the name of traditional style of authentic noodle..

Noodle 123 serves delicious noodles at an affordable price. I would like to give a special shoutout to the owner who is ever-patient in attending to customers' requests to ensure that each bowl of noodles is customised according to individual's preferences (& also for going an extra mile to remember customer's preferences for those who patronises his stall frequently)!

Will definitely recommend everyone to try it out :)!
